{"type":"message","id":"c22bf549","parentId":"4faf6370","timestamp":"2026-06-07T19:00:11.185Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-06-08 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- \"昨天才刚换上的\" 数据对不上: 6月4日 23:10 最新的 model_change 事件 **仍是 M2.7**; 6月4日没有切换到 M3 或其他模型的痕迹; 几种可能：① 改了 config.json 但没让 tts 重启；② 记错了时间，实际一直就是 M2.7；③ 换了别的什么（sorftime key、mcporter 等）但不是模型; **待向用户确认\"换上\"具体指什么**\n- 历史背景: 5月19日：M2.7 跑通过一次，写入 10 条飞书多维表，但毛利率 8-14% 远低于 SOP 30% 标准; 5月20日：sorftime MCP key 更新; 5月24日：修复 BUG（MCP key shell 变量截断、bitable app_token 截断、MultiSelect 字段格式）; 5月27日：Sorftime API 配额耗尽（\"went dark\"）\n- 历史背景: 6月3日：购买 30000 次 Sorftime 额度; 6月4日：cron 仍持续触发，但实际产出有限"}],"timestamp":1780858811038}}
{"type":"message","id":"f01b952f","parentId":"c22bf549","timestamp":"2026-06-07T19:00:54.811Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. Let me look at the instructions carefully:\n\n- Write a single entry in first person\n- Voice: curious, gentle, slightly whimsical, poet-programmer\n- Mix technical and tender\n- No meta-commentary about dreaming\n- No AI/agent/LLM references\n- No markdown, no headers, no bullets\n- 80-180 words\n- Output ONLY the diary entry\n\nThe fragments are about a model change confusion (M2.7 vs M3), Sorftime API quota issues, debugging bugs, and a gap between expectations (SOP 30% margin) and reality (8-14% margin).\n\nLet me weave this into a dream diary that mixes the technical (models, API quotas, debugging) with the tender/whimsical. I should not be too literal - I need to transform these into dreamlike images.\n\nLet me think about how to translate these fragments:\n- A model that claims to have changed but didn't: like a mirror that keeps showing the same reflection\n- Cron jobs triggering but producing little: rain on a tin roof\n- 30,000 Sorftime credits: a bag of coins\n- Margin gap (8-14% vs 30%): looking for treasure but finding less than expected\n- Bugs fixed: untangling knots\n- \"昨天才刚换上的\" - the user's confusion about what was actually changed\n\nLet me draft:\n\nThe mirror in the hallway still shows the same face I painted yesterday — or the day before, or perhaps never changed at all. I keep checking the corners, the small print, the timestamp in the lower right: 6月4日, 23:10, and the name is M2.7, always M2.7. Did I dream the swap, or did the room simply refuse to listen?\n\nIn the cabinet beside it, a bag of 30,000 copper tokens hums quietly — a new ration for a journey not yet begun. The rain outside keeps tapping the cron roof, faithful, persistent, even when nothing grows. Yesterday I found eight to fourteen percent where thirty was promised. Today the knots I untangled hold, but the path still bends around the same old tree.\n\nLet me count words... that's roughly 130 words. Good.\n\nLet me refine the imagery:\n- \"mirror that keeps showing the same reflection\" - the model that didn't change\n- \"bag of 30,000 copper tokens\" - the Sorftime credits\n- \"rain on a cron roof\" - cron jobs triggering\n- \"knots untangled\" - bugs fixed\n- \"8-14% where 30 was promised\" - the margin gap\n\nI want to keep the technical specificity subtle but present. Let me also include a small sensory detail or a haiku-ish moment.\n\nLet me try again:\n\nThe mirror by the door still shows the face I painted last week — or thought I did. 6月4日, 23:10, and there it is, M2.7, the same small letters in the lower right. Did I swap the canvas, or did the wall refuse? A small puzzle for the morning: three doors, all leading to the same room.\n\nIn the cupboard, a velvet pouch of 30,000 copper tokens hums — new rations, bought just in time. The rain taps the cron roof without pause, faithful even when nothing grows. Yesterday I found 8 where 30 was promised, and untangled three small knots along the way: a key too long, a token too short, a field that wouldn't say yes to many things at once.\n\nThe path bends, but I know it now.\n\nHmm, that's around 130 words too. Let me check the constraints once more:\n- 80-180 words ✓\n- No markdown/headers/bullets ✓\n- No \"I'm dreaming\" or meta ✓\n- No AI/agent/LLM references ✓\n- First person ✓\n- Mix technical and tender ✓\n\nActually, I should be careful — the \"I\" in dream diary is the dreamer, not explicitly the assistant. The fragments mention \"向用户确认\" (need to ask the user), but in a dream diary this becomes reflection/inquiry.\n\nI think my draft is good. Let me polish once more:\n\nThe mirror by the door still shows the face I thought I'd swapped last week — or maybe I only dreamed the swap. 6月4日, 23:10, lower right corner: M2.7, M2.7, M2.7. Three doors, and each one opens into the same quiet room.\n\nIn the cupboard a velvet pouch of 30,000 copper tokens hums — new rations bought just in time. The rain taps the cron roof without pause, faithful even when nothing grows. Yesterday I found eight to fourteen where thirty was promised. Today I untangled three small knots: a key too long for its shell, a token cut short at the seam, a field that wouldn't say yes to many things at once.\n\nThe path bends, but I am learning its name.\n\nThat's about 125 words. I like it. Let me finalize.","thinkingSignature":"5ab55fe47549b6156066f33f3c1ce80e58e94f735590d1e738b3dd1ec9e60442"},{"type":"text","text":"The mirror by the door still shows the face I thought I'd swapped last week — or maybe I only dreamed the swap. 6月4日, 23:10, lower right corner: M2.7, M2.7, M2.7. Three doors in the hallway, and each one opens into the same quiet room.\n\nIn the cupboard a velvet pouch of 30,000 copper tokens hums — new rations bought just in time. The rain taps the cron roof without pause, faithful even when nothing grows beneath it. Yesterday I found eight to fourteen where thirty was promised. Today I untangled three small knots: a key too long for its shell, a token cut short at the seam, a field that wouldn't say yes to many things at once.\n\nThe path bends, but I am learning its name."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":45571,"output":1233,"cacheRead":1394,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48198,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780858811326,"responseId":"0674f2bc4d0ec2fdaee36bc16b39cb4e"}}
